# Git Rules

## Branch Protection
### main
- Protected: true
- Requires review: true

### development
- Protected: true
- Requires review: true

## Commit Message Format
### Types
- feat: New feature
- fix: Bug fix
- docs: Documentation changes
- style: Code style changes
- refactor: Code refactoring
- test: Adding or modifying tests
- chore: Maintenance tasks

### Structure
- Type: Required
- Scope: Optional
- Subject: Required
- Body: Optional
- Footer: Optional

### Length Limits
- Subject: 72 characters
- Body: 100 characters

## Gitignore Patterns
- *.pyc
- __pycache__
- .env
- .DS_Store
- tmp/*
- results/*
- *.log
